There is nothing like cooking over an open fire. Unfortunately, that includes dealing with a dirty, greasy fire pit that cannot keep your utensils, spices, and condiments handy and still keep them clean. The Utensil Tree solves the problem all by itself. It keeps everything you need at your fingertips, but out of the way from children and up off the ground. It has an 8 inch diameter tray and drainage holes for rain and spill. Constructed with a scalloped top keeps items from rolling off. The adjustable height 3-pronged utensil hook will meet anyones desired height. There is also a step bar with two heavy duty 6 inch prongs that pushes in the ground with your foot. The tray keeps beverages and condiments handy. It is the perfect campfire assistant.Zippo Utensil Tree

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
